docs.text: Community Site This content isn't part of the main site , it's maintained by a community content editor. When changes to this site are pushed to github , a CodePipeline job is executed to build and deploy a new container to AWS ECS. In this container, I've configured apache "AllowOverride" to "All". This gives the content editor basic control over access to the content they present. I have some important stuff for you to see if you know the password...
